   "source": [
    "# Project Folder Structure\n",
    "This structure separates our workspaces purposefully:\n",
    "* **data/**: Stores our raw and processed data so they don't get accidentally overwritten.\n",
    "* **notebooks/**: Contains interactive exploratory data analysis files (.ipynb).\n",
    "* **scripts/**: Holds python files (.py) for complex reusable logic.\n",
    "* **outputs/**: The destination for graphs, figures, and exports.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Why this matters:\n",
    "By not blending data, notebooks, and outputs, the repository avoids broken file paths and lost files."
